 AmiTradeCenter V1.2 (short ATC) / powerful FREE FTP-Client with ADT Support
{pp}
 This release is mainly due, because of some confusions regarding v1.1 and
 v1.1 PreRelease8 (which came later than v1.1).
{pp}
 . parser for standard ftp-URL like ftp://anonymous:JohnDoe@unknown.org@ftp.uni-paderborn.de:21!{p}
 . let you change the directory and file permissions on certain servers (CHMOD)!{p}
 . reorder and edit downloadbatch before and during the transfer!{p}
 . separate dir-history and statistics for every server!{p}
 . Additional execution of scripts on certain events!{p}
 . upload a complete dir-tree to a ftp-server!{p}
 . mirror complete servers on your harddisk!{p}
 . acoustic signals for every action!{p}
 . tetris for long downloads!{p}
 . nice cps history!{p}
 . aminet charts!{p}
 . rate files!
